
- Offline Dino
- Upgrades / Achievements
	- Gun
		- Allows killing Pterodactyl and Triceratops
		- 1 bullet every second
		- Unlocked by "100 Jumps in a row!"
	- Machine Gun
		- Upgrades Gun
		- 5 bullets every second
		- Unlocked by "Kill 20 Pterodactyls"
	- Boots
		- Allow double jump
		- Jump into a Pterodactyl
	- Armor
		- Die 10 times
		- Allow 1 extra life
	- Beat Triceratops
		- Unlock Nier Pod

- Modes
	- Endless Mode
	- Story Mode
		- Requires at least a Gun
- Goal
	- Kill Triceratops
		- Requires at leat Gun
	
	
